#. <section class="sutta" id="mn151"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn151:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 151"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 151"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn151:0.2"
msgid "Piṇḍapātapārisuddhisutta"
msgstr "The Purification of Alms"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn151:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

msgctxt "mn151:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
"Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, Sāriputta came out of retreat and went to the "
"Buddha. He bowed and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.294"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Vippasannāni kho te, sāriputta, indriyāni, parisuddho chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto."
msgstr ""
"“Sāriputta, your faculties are so very clear, and your complexion is pure "
"and bright."

#. VAR: bahulaṃ → etarahi bahulaṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "mn151:2.2"
msgid "Katamena kho tvaṃ, sāriputta, vihārena etarahi bahulaṃ viharasī”ti?"
msgstr "What kind of meditation are you usually practicing these days?”"

msgctxt "mn151:2.3"
msgid "“Suññatāvihārena kho ahaṃ, bhante, etarahi bahulaṃ viharāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Sir, these days I usually practice the meditation on emptiness.”"

msgctxt "mn151:2.4"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, sāriputta."
msgstr "“Good, good, Sāriputta!"

msgctxt "mn151:2.5"
msgid "Mahāpurisavihārena kira tvaṃ, sāriputta, etarahi bahulaṃ viharasi."
msgstr "It seems you usually practice the meditation of a great man."

#. VAR: eso → hesa (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "mn151:2.6"
msgid "Mahāpurisavihāro eso, sāriputta, yadidaṃ—"
msgstr "For emptiness is the meditation of a great man."

msgctxt "mn151:2.7"
msgid "suññatā."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, sāriputta, bhikkhu sace ākaṅkheyya:"
msgstr "Now, a mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn151:3.2"
msgid ""
"‘suññatāvihārena bahulaṃ vihareyyan’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti "
"paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"‘May I usually practice the meditation on emptiness.’ So they should reflect:"

msgctxt "mn151:3.3"
msgid ""
"‘yena cāhaṃ maggena gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ, yasmiñca padese piṇḍāya acariṃ, "
"yena ca maggena gāmato piṇḍāya paṭikkamiṃ, atthi nu kho me tattha "
"cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu chando vā rāgo vā doso vā moho vā paṭighaṃ vāpi "
"cetaso’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Along the path that I went for alms, or in the place I wandered for alms, "
"or along the path that I returned from alms, was there any desire or greed "
"or hate or delusion or repulsion in my heart for sights known by the eye?’"

msgctxt "mn151:3.4"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:3.5"
msgid ""
"‘yena cāhaṃ maggena gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ, yasmiñca padese piṇḍāya acariṃ, "
"yena ca maggena gāmato piṇḍāya paṭikkamiṃ, atthi me tattha cakkhuviññeyyesu "
"rūpesu chando vā rāgo vā doso vā moho vā paṭighaṃ vāpi cetaso’ti, tena, "
"sāriputta, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya "
"vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"there was such desire or greed or hate or delusion or repulsion in their "
"heart, they should make an effort to give up those unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "mn151:3.6"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:3.7"
msgid ""
"‘yena cāhaṃ maggena gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ, yasmiñca padese piṇḍāya acariṃ, "
"yena ca maggena gāmato piṇḍāya paṭikkamiṃ, natthi me tattha cakkhuviññeyyesu "
"rūpesu chando vā rāgo vā doso vā moho vā paṭighaṃ vāpi cetaso’ti, tena, "
"sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā "
"kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"there was no such desire or greed or hate or delusion or repulsion in their "
"heart, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in "
"skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4-8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.295"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:4-8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant should reflect:"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.2"
msgid ""
"‘yena cāhaṃ maggena gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ, yasmiñca padese piṇḍāya acariṃ, "
"yena ca maggena gāmato piṇḍāya paṭikkamiṃ, atthi nu kho me tattha "
"sotaviññeyyesu saddesu … pe …"
msgstr ""
"‘Along the path that I went for alms, or in the place I wandered for alms, "
"or along the path that I returned from alms, was there any desire or greed "
"or hate or delusion or repulsion in my heart for sounds known by the ear …"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.3"
msgid "ghānaviññeyyesu gandhesu …"
msgstr "smells known by the nose …"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.4"
msgid "jivhāviññeyyesu rasesu …"
msgstr "tastes known by the tongue …"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.5"
msgid "kāyaviññeyyesu phoṭṭhabbesu …"
msgstr "touches known by the body …"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.6"
msgid ""
"manoviññeyyesu dhammesu chando vā rāgo vā doso vā moho vā paṭighaṃ vāpi "
"cetaso’ti?"
msgstr "thoughts known by the mind?’"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.7"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.8"
msgid ""
"‘yena cāhaṃ maggena gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ, yasmiñca padese piṇḍāya acariṃ, "
"yena ca maggena gāmato piṇḍāya paṭikkamiṃ, atthi me tattha manoviññeyyesu "
"dhammesu chando vā rāgo vā doso vā moho vā paṭighaṃ vāpi cetaso’ti, tena, "
"sāriputta, bhikkhunā tesaṃyeva pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya "
"vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"there was such desire or greed or hate or delusion or repulsion in their "
"heart, they should make an effort to give up those unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.9"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:4-8.10"
msgid ""
"‘yena cāhaṃ maggena gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ, yasmiñca padese piṇḍāya acariṃ, "
"yena ca maggena gāmato piṇḍāya paṭikkamiṃ, natthi me tattha manoviññeyyesu "
"dhammesu chando vā rāgo vā doso vā moho vā paṭighaṃ vāpi cetaso’ti, tena, "
"sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā "
"kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"there was no such desire or greed or hate or delusion or repulsion in their "
"heart, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training day and night in "
"skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:9.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant should reflect:"

msgctxt "mn151:9.2"
msgid "‘pahīnā nu kho me pañca kāmaguṇā’ti?"
msgstr "‘Have I given up the five kinds of sensual stimulation?’"

msgctxt "mn151:9.3"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:9.4"
msgid ""
"‘appahīnā kho me pañca kāmaguṇā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā pañcannaṃ "
"kāmaguṇānaṃ pahānāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr "they have not given them up, they should make an effort to do so."

msgctxt "mn151:9.5"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:9.6"
msgid ""
"‘pahīnā kho me pañca kāmaguṇā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"they have given them up, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training "
"day and night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:10.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
