"pañcannaṃ upādānakkhandhānaṃ pariññāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"they have not completely understood them, they should make an effort to do "
"so."

msgctxt "mn151:11.5"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:11.6"
msgid ""
