"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"they have completely understood them, they should meditate with rapture and "
"joy, training day and night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:12.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant should reflect:"

msgctxt "mn151:12.2"
msgid "‘bhāvitā nu kho me cattāro satipaṭṭhānā’ti?"
msgstr "‘Have I developed the four kinds of mindfulness meditation?’"

msgctxt "mn151:12.3"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:12.4"
msgid ""
