msgctxt "mn151:18.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn151:18.2"
msgid "‘bhāvito nu kho me ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo’ti?"
msgstr "the noble eightfold path?’"

msgctxt "mn151:18.3"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:18.4"
msgid ""
"‘abhāvito kho me ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā "
"ariyassa aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa bhāvanāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr "they haven’t developed it, they should make an effort to do so."

msgctxt "mn151:18.5"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:18.6"
msgid ""
"‘bhāvito kho me ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"they have developed it, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training "
"day and night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:19.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant should reflect:"

msgctxt "mn151:19.2"
msgid "‘bhāvitā nu kho me samatho ca vipassanā cā’ti?"
msgstr "‘Have I developed serenity and discernment?’"

msgctxt "mn151:19.3"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:19.4"
msgid ""
"‘abhāvitā kho me samatho ca vipassanā cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā "
"samathavipassanānaṃ bhāvanāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr "they haven’t developed them, they should make an effort to do so."

msgctxt "mn151:19.5"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:19.6"
msgid ""
"‘bhāvitā kho me samatho ca vipassanā cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā "
"teneva pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"they have developed them, they should meditate with rapture and joy, "
"training day and night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:20.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, sāriputta, bhikkhunā iti paṭisañcikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "Furthermore, a mendicant should reflect:"

msgctxt "mn151:20.2"
msgid "‘sacchikatā nu kho me vijjā ca vimutti cā’ti?"
msgstr "‘Have I realized knowledge and freedom?’"

msgctxt "mn151:20.3"
msgid "Sace, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "Suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:20.4"
msgid ""
"‘asacchikatā kho me vijjā ca vimutti cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā "
"vijjāya vimuttiyā sacchikiriyāya vāyamitabbaṃ."
msgstr "they haven’t realized them, they should make an effort to do so."

msgctxt "mn151:20.5"
msgid "Sace pana, sāriputta, bhikkhu paccavekkhamāno evaṃ jānāti:"
msgstr "But suppose that, upon checking, a mendicant knows that"

msgctxt "mn151:20.6"
msgid ""
"‘sacchikatā kho me vijjā ca vimutti cā’ti, tena, sāriputta, bhikkhunā teneva "
"pītipāmojjena vihātabbaṃ ahorattānusikkhinā kusalesu dhammesu."
msgstr ""
"they have realized them, they should meditate with rapture and joy, training "
"day and night in skillful qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:21.1"
msgid ""
"Ye hi keci, sāriputta, atītamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhesuṃ, sabbe te evameva paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"Whether in the past, future, or present, all those who purify their alms-"
"food do so by continually checking in this way."

msgctxt "mn151:21.2"
msgid ""
"Yepi hi keci, sāriputta, anāgatamaddhānaṃ samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhessanti, sabbe te evameva paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhessanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn151:21.3"
msgid ""
"Yepi hi keci, sāriputta, etarahi samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhenti, sabbe te evameva paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhenti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: Tasmātiha, sāriputta → tena hi vo sāriputta evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ (bj, pts1) | tasmātiha vo sāriputta sikkhitabbaṃ (s1, s2) | tasmātiha vo sārīputta sikkhitabbaṃ (s3)
msgctxt "mn151:21.4"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, sāriputta, ‘paccavekkhitvā paccavekkhitvā piṇḍapātaṃ "
"parisodhessāmā’ti—"
msgstr ""
"So, Sāriputta, you should all train like this: ‘We shall purify our alms-"
"food by continually checking.’”"

msgctxt "mn151:21.5"
msgid "evañhi vo, sāriputta, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn151:21.6"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn151:21.7"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā sāriputto bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Sāriputta was happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn151:21.8"
msgid "Piṇḍapātapārisuddhisuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
